ze == max(sizes)]\n    smallest_blocks = [block for block in black_blocks if block.size == min(sizes)]\n    return (np.array(largest_blocks), np.array(smallest_blocks))", "holes": {"identity": "same as input grid", "replace_smallest_blocks_with_teal": "replace the smallest blocks with color teal in output_grid ", "find_black_blocks": "there are different blocks seperated by red element, there are rectangle ,you need to find all blocks of black element", "replace_largest_blocks_with_blue": "replace the largest blocks with color blue in output grid ", "find_largest_and_smallest_blocks": "find the largest and smallest blocks in black_blocks"}}
